{
    "poem_title": "- XLIX - Colérico amor ",
    "corpus": "adso",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "author": "Pedro Soto de Rojas",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "n": "1",
                    "line_text": "¿Por qué Fénix permites, que padezca,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-++--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "n": "2",
                    "line_text": "(siendo tú causa) este dolor extraño?",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+++--+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "n": "3",
                    "line_text": "si es por no merecerte, no es engaño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-+--+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "n": "4",
                    "line_text": "que por nacer está quien te merezca.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "¿Por qué Fénix permites, que padezca,\n(siendo tú causa) este dolor extraño?\nsi es por no merecerte, no es engaño,\nque por nacer está quien te merezca."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "n": "5",
                    "line_text": "No, que soy tan indigno te parezca,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+-++-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "n": "6",
                    "line_text": "aunque (cual ves) me cubre tosco paño,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "n": "7",
                    "line_text": "que no confiere amor (cuando es tamaño)",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+-+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "n": "8",
                    "line_text": "que vil materia sus ardores crezca.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "No, que soy tan indigno te parezca,\naunque (cual ves) me cubre tosco paño,\nque no confiere amor (cuando es tamaño)\nque vil materia sus ardores crezca."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "n": "9",
                    "line_text": "Sacrificado a tu belleza pura",
                    "metrical_pattern": "---+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "n": "10",
                    "line_text": "tienes mi pecho, admite sus ardores,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "n": "11",
                    "line_text": "si has de admitirlos, de mortal criatura;",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sacrificado a tu belleza pura\ntienes mi pecho, admite sus ardores,\nsi has de admitirlos, de mortal criatura;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "n": "12",
                    "line_text": "y si han de merecer tus amadores,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "n": "13",
                    "line_text": "por valor natural tu hermosura,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "n": "14",
                    "line_text": "tú sola ten a tu belleza amores.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "y si han de merecer tus amadores,\npor valor natural tu hermosura,\ntú sola ten a tu belleza amores."
        }
    ]
}